    section#main
      h1 Precision Machining Shop
      p
        | Welcome to the Precision Machine shop at West-MEC! Support our CTSO by buying our products. All money
        | gained from the shop is put to good use, being used to send students to state and nationals, and
        | fund other CTSO related activities.
      // 3 divs with the class of menu item, each having a div with the id of the item it's holding, followed by a picture of the item and then the information. Ater that it has a div that holds two more divs for the buttons, add and remove.
      section#items
        .menuItem
          #keychain
            img(src='img/keychain.jpg' alt='')
            h1 Keychain
            p
              | Show off your support for our CTSO buy buying our exclusive keyring. It&apos;s both cheap and
              | stylish, so order one now and show it around!
            p
              strong
                em Cost: $2
          .shopButtons
            .add
              button Add to Order
            .remove
              button Remove Item
        .menuItem
          #vicegrip
            img(src='img/vicegrip.jpg' alt='')
            h1 Vice Grip
            p
              | Buy one of our specially branded vice grips, good for both students and anyone else doing
              | handy work to buy.
            p
              strong
                em Cost: $7
          .shopButtons
            .add
              button Add to Order
            .remove
              button Remove Item
        .menuItem
          #pens
            img(src='img/pens.png' alt='')
            h1 Pens
            p
              | Specially designed, black inc pens. Get them in a pack of 5 and show your support for our
              | CTSO!
            p
              strong
                em Cost: $5
          .shopButtons
            .add
              button Add to Order
            .remove
              button Remove Item
      #checkout
        button
          img(src='img/cart.jpg' alt='cart')
